## Attach Employees to Workspace

```shell
curl -X "POST" "http://<%= config[:base_url] %>/workspaces/<WORKSPACE_ID>/relationships/employees" \\
     -H 'x-api-key: <%= config[:api_key] %>' \\
     -H 'tio-auth-token: <%= config[:api_token] %>' \\
     -H 'Content-Type: application/vnd.api+json' \\
     -d $'{
        "data": [{
          "id": "1",
          "type": "employees"
        }]
}'
```


This endpoint attaches a single employee to a specific workspace.

<aside class="success">
  Employees may only belong to a single workspace
</aside>

### HTTP Request

`POST <%= config[:base_url]%>/workspaces/<ID>/relationships/employees`


## Remove Employees from Workspace
```shell
curl -X "DELETE" "http://<%= config[:base_url] %>/workspaces/<WORKSPACE_ID>/relationships/employees" \\
     -H 'x-api-key: <%= config[:api_key] %>' \\
     -H 'tio-auth-token: <%= config[:api_token] %>' \\
     -H 'Content-Type: application/vnd.api+json' \\
     -d $'{
        "data": [{
          "id": "1",
          "type": "employees"
        }]
      }'
```

> Returns "204 No Content" on success


This endpoint removes a single employee to a specific workspace.
